## Naming Conventions

| Type | Convention | Example |
|---|---|---|
| Component | PascalCase | `StoreCard.tsx` |
| Screen | PascalCase + `Screen` | `MarketMapScreen.tsx` |
| Hook | camelCase + `use` prefix | `useNearbyStores.ts` |
| Service | camelCase + `Service` | `krogerService.ts` |
| Zustand store | camelCase + `Store` | `useCartStore.ts` |
| Type/Interface | PascalCase | `Store`, `IngredientItem` |
| Constant | UPPER_SNAKE | `MAX_STORE_RADIUS_MILES` |

