## Styling Rules

```tsx
// ✅ StyleSheet.create — all styles at the bottom of file
const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  card: {
    backgroundColor: Colors.surfaceContainerLowest,
    borderRadius: 16,
    padding: 16,
  },
});

// ❌ Inline object styles — creates new object on every render
<View style={{ backgroundColor: '#fff', padding: 16 }} />
```

- **All colors** from `Colors` (`utils/colors.ts`) — never hardcode hex
- **No magic numbers** — extract to named constant if used >1 time
- **Shadows:** always set both `shadowColor/shadowOffset/shadowOpacity/shadowRadius` (iOS) **and** `elevation` (Android)
- **Absolute positioning** always requires `zIndex` documented with a comment

