## @rnmapbox/maps Hygiene

```tsx
// ✅ Initialize token ONCE at app startup (App.tsx)
import MapboxGL from '@rnmapbox/maps';
MapboxGL.setAccessToken(process.env.EXPO_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_ACCESS_TOKEN!);

// ✅ Lazy-load map screens — heavy WebGL context
const MarketMapScreen = React.lazy(() => import('./screens/MarketMapScreen'));

// ✅ Cap markers — cluster beyond 50 pins
import Supercluster from 'supercluster';
// render clusters, not raw markers

// ✅ Traffic-aware routing via Directions API
const route = await mapboxDirections.getRoute({
  profile: 'driving-traffic',
  waypoints: [origin, ...stops],
});

// ❌ Never leave map mounted after navigation
useEffect(() => {
  return () => map.current?.remove(); // cleanup WebGL context
}, []);
```

- Map view must show a **loading placeholder** while tiles load
- `Camera` component handles viewport — never manipulate `flyTo` without user intent
- Store marker click → update carousel selection, do NOT trigger re-render of entire map

